content: Due to a crash on the Pacific Highway at Lake Haven Drive, some buses are being delayed.
subtitle: Some delays in Lake Haven

properties.speechText: In Lake Haven, some buses and school services are delayed up to 15 minutes due to a crash on the Pacific Highway at Lake Haven Drive.
